# ViewModels/Base Directory
# 
# This directory should contain base/abstract ViewModels:
# - BaseViewModel.swift (common ViewModel functionality)
# - LoadableViewModel.swift (loading states, error handling)
# - ListViewModel.swift (base for list/collection ViewModels)
# - FormViewModel.swift (base for form-based ViewModels)
# - NavigationViewModel.swift (navigation coordination)
# 
# Base ViewModels provide reusable functionality and establish
# common patterns for state management across the app